info.name: Time Out Armchair
info.description: Family of outdoor furnishings made from rotationally-moulded polyethylene and steel structures. The collection is made up of: a chair, an armchair, a stool, and a chaise longue that is available in both a fixed version and a reclinable version. From April 2013 is also available in the stylish combination with Hiroko Wood structure (also for outdoor use)
